channel.title: Help with removing a wall
channel.description:
[b][i]Well I have removed the Pillars and Mysterious Glow objects in the Mind-RuneCrafting temple. I just need to know now how to remove a wall? Don't tell me to search I already have, don't tell me to look in tutorials section I spent a while looking through them about 3-4 times. Would be great.[/b]
[IMG]http://img299.imageshack.us/img299/2784/how.png[/img]

item.title: Help with removing a wall
item.dc:creator: @Rockin Rockin
item.description:
@Rockin wrote:

I’m not 100% sure, but this should work:

Look for

public void Deleteobjects() {

Under that you should see stuff like this

 	       deletethatobject(2611, 3095);
 	       deletethatobject(2611, 3097);
 	       deletethatobject(2612, 3097);

Make a new “deletethatobject” and put the cords of the wall inside the ()

Hope I helped
